  "body": "- [x] I've asked for help  ~~in the [Truffle Gitter](http://gitter.im/Consensys/truffle)~~ directly with @gnidan  before filing this issue.\r\n\r\n---------------------------\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\n- Unable to specify a custom polling interval\r\n- Would like to be able to do so in order to reduce the \"chattiness\"  over JSON-RPC\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n- N/A - this is a request to improve an existing feature\r\n\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nEither of the following options:\r\n\r\n(1) Modify `HDWalletProvider` to accept a `pollingInterval` argument [during instantiation](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/tree/master/packages/hdwallet-provider#instantiation).\r\n\r\n(2) Modify Truffle network config to accept a `pollingInterval` argument [in config file](https://www.trufflesuite.com/docs/truffle/reference/configuration#networks)\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\n- N/A this is a request to improve an existing feature\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: ubuntu 18.04\r\n* Ethereum client: rskj 2.0.1\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): truffle 5.1.22\r\n* node version (`node --version`): node 12.16.1\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): npm 6.14.4\r\n\r\n## References\r\n\r\n- [Stackoverflow question](https://stackoverflow.com/q/64656558/194982)\r\n- [HDWalletProvider docs for instantiation](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle/tree/master/packages/hdwallet-provider#instantiation)\r\n- [Truffle network config docs](https://www.trufflesuite.com/docs/truffle/reference/configuration#networks)\r\n- (Currently unmaintained) [implementation](https://github.com/DigixGlobal/truffle-lightwallet-provider/blob/9acb7f86a92deedba2d8a1d2beac95db26aa7071/src/index.js#L23-L24) which is similar to HDWalletProvider\r\n",
